               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡, Image of the Savior of the World, መልክአ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="18r" facs="003">Fols 1r–18r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2927RepCh208">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                     <incipit>ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
