                    <locus from="23r" to="31r" facs="025">Fols 23r–31r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2965RepCh246">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Gabrǝʾel</title>
                    <incipit>ሰላመ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡ በላዕለ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘአዕረፈ።<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
